description: A cartoon image depicts a blonde, light-skinned nun slumped over a wooden confessional. The nun is wearing a traditional dark purple habit, a white wimple framing her face, and black shoes. Her left hand dangles off the side of the confessional, her fingers pointing downwards, and she has black nail polish. Her head rests on the top of the confessional. The confessional is made of orange-brown wood with simple lines and a small triangular window. At the base of the confessional, an open book with cream-colored pages rests on the floor, held open by a thin red ribbon. The overall impression is one of humor and perhaps a touch of irreverence.
